{"tid":2053161,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港版國安法：英擬擴大持BNO港人權利　中方或出招反制","createTime":"2020-06-06T05:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T16:59:10.000Z","uid":66271,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4059b8ea5a87cdfe0ca4690911a79c589e9e6e83","tid":2053161,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:03:25.000Z","msg":"「港版國安法」引爆激烈政治角力，英國首相約翰遜及外相藍韜文多次提到中方若繼續立法，便會考慮擴大持BNO的港人權利，最終獲得居留權機會。有政界消息指，英國一旦落實相關措施，中央或會出招反制，包括取消BNO持有人的中國國籍、香港居留權及投票權。<br />\n<br />\n政界消息認為，英國政府在香港民主問題上指手畫腳，如果英政府最終決定BNO護照持有人是英國公民，不排除中央會作出回應，包括宣布接受英國政府單方面安排的港人，會自動喪失中國國籍和香港居留權，有關港人的投票權亦可能被取消。"},{"pid":"478f1cb827294f17adcdbb571355b257f501ebe9","tid":2053161,"uid":31773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"又黎豪賭一鋪<br />\n<br />\n大陸仲未輸夠？<br />\n<br />\n又話留島不留人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40370035fdbf6843795df2249bf9e0fa518c1097","tid":2053161,"uid":44323,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"取消BNO持有人的中國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faacac6cfc03978c291cf605826cba1565d09b85","tid":2053161,"uid":326700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:05:53.000Z","msg":"點出招?俾英國人有中國國籍?"},{"pid":"5d8225798cd7e396a9c77f3af648f944c037fa75","tid":2053161,"uid":33028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"喪失中國國籍=直接變BC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aadda4c11d81c7e70fa035b8bb087e21dc367e","tid":2053161,"uid":26708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5